  "local_port": 57890,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Which are the best ad agencies in Barcelona?",
  "response": "Barcelona is a vibrant hub for creativity and innovation, home to numerous top-tier advertising agencies that cater to a diverse range of clients and industries. Here are some of the best ad agencies in Barcelona, known for their creativity, strategic thinking, and impactful campaigns:\n\n### 1. **Shackleton**\n- **Overview:** Renowned for their bold and unconventional campaigns, Shackleton has built a reputation for pushing creative boundaries.\n- **Notable Clients:** Seat, T\u00e8rmens, Totto\n- **Website:** [shackleton.com](https://www.shackleton.com/)\n\n### 2. **SCPF (Semiconductor Concept Program Framework)**\n- **Overview:** SCPF focuses on strategic creativity, delivering integrated marketing solutions that combine innovation with effectiveness.\n- **Notable Clients:** BMW, Fanta, Emirates\n- **Website:** [scpf.com](https://scpf.com/)\n\n### 3. **Ter\u00e1n\\TBWA**\n- **Overview:** Part of the global TBWA network, Ter\u00e1n\\TBWA excels in disruptive advertising strategies that challenge the status quo.\n- **Notable Clients:** Adidas, Audi, McDonald's\n- **Website:** [terantbwa.com](https://www.terantbwa.com/)\n\n### 4. **Futurapic**\n- **Overview:** Specializing in digital marketing and creative solutions, Futurapic offers services ranging from branding to multimedia production.\n- **Notable Clients:** Netflix, Mango, Seat\n- **Website:** [futurapic.com](https://futurapic.com/)\n\n### 5. **McCann Barcelona**\n- **Overview:** Part of the global McCann network, McCann Barcelona provides comprehensive advertising services with a focus on strategic excellence.\n- **Notable Clients:** Coca-Cola, L'Or\u00e9al, Microsoft\n- **Website:** [mccann.es](https://www.mccann.es/)\n\n### 6. **Ogilvy Barcelona**\n- **Overview:** Ogilvy is a global leader in advertising and marketing, offering integrated solutions that combine creativity with data-driven strategies.\n- **Notable Clients:** Ford, Nestl\u00e9, Samsung\n- **Website:** [ogilvy.com](https://www.ogilvy.com/offices/barcelona)\n\n### 7. **Leo Burnett Barcelona**\n- **Overview:** Known for their human-centered approach, Leo Burnett creates meaningful and emotionally resonant campaigns.\n- **Notable Clients:** Procter & Gamble, Kellogg's, McDonald's\n- **Website:** [leoburnett.com](https://leoburnett.com/offices/barcelona/)\n\n### 8. **Havas Barcelona**\n- **Overview:** Havas offers a wide range of advertising and communication services, emphasizing creativity and innovation.\n- **Notable Clients:** Citro\u00ebn, Adidas, LVMH\n- **Website:** [havas.com](https://www.havas.com/locations/spain/barcelona/)\n\n### 9. **VMLY&R Barcelona**\n- **Overview:** VMLY&R combines branding, marketing, and technology to create integrated and impactful campaigns.\n- **Notable Clients:** Colgate, Ford, Wendy's\n- **Website:** [vmlryr.com](https://www.vmlyr.com/en/locations/barcelona)\n\n### 10. **Grey Barcelona**\n- **Overview:** Part of the global Grey network, Grey Barcelona is known for its creative excellence and strategic marketing solutions.\n- **Notable Clients:** Procter & Gamble, Canon, Volvo\n- **Website:** [grey.com](https://www.grey.com/barcelona)\n\n### Honorable Mentions\n\n- **DDB Spain:** Known for creative advertising and strategic communication.\n- **La Despensa:** Focuses on innovative and culturally relevant campaigns.\n- **Moment Factory:** Specializes in multimedia and immersive experiences.\n\nWhen selecting an ad agency, consider factors such as the agency's expertise in your industry, their creative portfolio, client testimonials, and how well their services align with your business objectives. Visiting their websites and reaching out for consultations can provide further insights to help you make an informed decision.",
